<%@taglib prefix="fn" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/functions"%>
<%@taglib prefix="fmt" uri="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/fmt"%>
<DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta content="initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no,maximum-scale=1,width=device-width" name="viewport" />
<meta content="yes" name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" />
<meta content="black" name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" />
<meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>${company }</title>
<!-- CSS -->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${cxt}/static/css/common.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${cxt}/static/css/base.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${cxt}/static/css/showcase.css">
<style>
body {
	background-color: #f9f9f9;
}
</style>
<script src="${cxt}/static/js/Crow5.sjs.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<body class=" ">
	<!-- container -->
	<div class="container ">
		<div class="content js-mini-height">
			<div class="content-body">
				<!-- 标题 -->
				<div>
					<div class="custom-title  text-left">
						<h2 class="title">我要推广</h2>
						<p class="sub_title">${company }</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="custom-richtext">
					<strong>您的邀请码是：</strong>
					<p>
						<font color="red" size="14px">${counselor.invitecode }</font>
					</p>
					<strong>邀请步骤：</strong>
					<p>
						1）请将您的邀请码【<font color="red">${counselor.invitecode }</font>】告知您要推广的用户。
					</p>
					<p>
						2）让您的推广用户关注<font color="red">${gzhname }</font>服务号，微信号为【<font color="red">${gzh }</font>】。
					</p>
					<p>
						3）成功关注后，点击<font color="red">账户</font>菜单下的<font color="red">我的信息</font>进行注册绑定。
					</p>
					<p>
						4）输入基本信息和您的邀请码【<font color="red">${counselor.invitecode }</font>】提交完成注册绑定。
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<footer style="margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px">
		<p align="center">&copy; ${company }</p>
	</footer>
</body>
</html>